data.description:
Experience Tryon luxury just a mile from Harmon Fields park on a private 2.5 +/- acre estate. This
3,600 sq ft masterpiece boasts stone-walled gardens, mature trees, a serene creek, and back-to-back wood-burning fireplaces. The updated kitchen features custom Oklahoma Walnut cabinets,
vaulted ceilings, and garden views. A den/office with Mahogany built-ins adds sophistication.
A 928 sq ft workshop, with power, plumbing, lighting, and heat, invites creativity. Connected
by a covered breezeway porch, it's perfect for a studio or an easy buildout of a guest
cottage. You must see this home to truly appreciate all of its features, design, and quality.
